{
  "stem": "3100.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they took it over, and they worked on parts for airplanes there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after 1942, at one time-- or it was in the beginning of '43-- some of-- of us tried to organize to escape from there knowing that there was no way to escape.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they started to dig a tunnel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And somehow by coincidence, they caught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in one day, they shot about 75 or 80 people in that camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And of course, that brought again a great fear and terror to the rest of us that were left.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you know how it felt, people you know that they were shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were the mostly shot around the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they built a-- a toilet, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That took 40, 50 people could go in at one time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that toilet, most of the people there were shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- you know, every time, my brother and I, we thank God that we weren't among them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we kept on going just to sustain ourselves to be able to live through hoping that the time will come when we will be freed from there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the end-- also at one time, at the beginning in 1943 in June-- in January or February, they took us out from that camp because they found out it was too much in the woods.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And therefore, there were some partisans",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--happenings.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us out, and put us in striped clothes, and declared that we are now no more in a working camp, but in a konzentrationslager, a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then at that time, everybody was given--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two letters, a K and an L, which means konzentrationslager.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
